ok	0	Success
usage_error	2	Bad arguments or invalid option values
not_configured	4	APR project is not initialized
config_error	4	Workflow, config, or filesystem configuration problem
validation_failed	4	Precondition failed before running
dependency_missing	3	Required local dependency is unavailable
busy	12	Single-flight lock or busy state blocks this operation
network_error	10	Remote or network operation failed
update_error	11	Self-update failed
attachment_mismatch	4	Attachment or file manifest mismatch
not_implemented	1	Requested feature is not supported in this install
internal_error	1	Unexpected APR bug or unknown state
